10. Example: AI prompt tracing in CFM-1

User prompt:
“Give me a math power tier ranking”

Field

Possible response modes:
{ [school-math], [prestige-ranking], [capability-ranking], [humor-ranking] }

Gates
	•	|> answers-user-intent
	•	|> matches-user-style
	•	|> gives-structure
	•	|> interesting

Survivor

[capability-ranking] !!

That’s basically what happened.

So this language can describe not only math problems, but model behavior.

